Previous Experience

An experienced leader and manager with over thirty years of experience as a pilot in the exacting environment of military fast jet operations and commercial widebody aviation. I am used to leading and managing teams of professionals to stringent performance targets where flexibility and an ability to find viable solutions in often-compressed time frames is key. Attention is always paid to the details but without losing focus on the bigger picture.
